       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI84104.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI84104.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Manutençăo de Despesas                                     *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI84104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3605 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6702 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01 WS-SQL-AUXILIARY.
         05 IND-NULL                       PIC S9(04) BINARY.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV8410.
       COPY COCV8411.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY ETCK0001.
       COPY ETCK0002.
       COPY COCL5005.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT3605 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3605'.
           05 CON-COVT6702 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6702'.
           05 CON-AT       PIC X(02) VALUE 'AT'.
           05 CON-999      PIC X(03) VALUE '999'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI84104'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI84104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV8410-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8410-ASE               TO COCV8411-ASE.

           INITIALIZE COCL5005-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                              ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
           MOVE SPACES                     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
           MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
           MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
           MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
           MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN          TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8410-ADE               TO COCV8411-ADE.


           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA
                 THRU 2399-OBTEM-CEMPRESA-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
                 THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV8410-CIMPOSTO     NOT = SPACES
             AND COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT NOT = ZEROS
                PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
                   THRU 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-INSERE-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                 2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA.

            IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
               MOVE '2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
               PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                  THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
            END-IF.


            MOVE COCV8410-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO.
      *RR   MOVE COCV8410-GFORNECED     TO COCD3605-CLIENTE.

            EXEC SQL
                  SELECT  CEMPRESA, PAIS
                    INTO :COCD3605-CEMPRESA, :COCD3605-PAIS
                  FROM    COVT3605_PROJECTS
                  WHERE   NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
      *RR           AND   CLIENTE     = :COCD3605-CLIENTE
            END-EXEC.

            MOVE CON-COVT3605 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
            PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
               THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV8411-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-N-EXISTS
                   TO COCV8411-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV8411-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.


       2399-OBTEM-CEMPRESA-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF  COCV8410-REFINVOICE(6:3) = CON-999
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-REFINV-999
                   TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV8410-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATDP-AUTO
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV     TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                          TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF  COCV8410-MVOR         = ZEROS
              AND COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT = ZEROS
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV8411-MVOR-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-VALOR-OBRIGAT
                   TO COCV8411-MVOR-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV8411-MVOR-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF  COCV8410-REFINVOICE NOT = SPACES
              AND COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT = ZEROS
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV8411-NTOTALAMOUNT-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-VALOR-OBRIGAT
                   TO COCV8411-NTOTALAMOUNT-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV8411-NTOTALAMOUNT-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.
**AF  * Deixa de obrigar a preencher a referencia
**AF  *
**AF  *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
**AF  *      IF  COCV8410-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB
**AF  *      AND COCV8410-REFINVOICE EQUAL SPACES
**AF  *      OR  COCV8410-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATDP-PAG
**AF  *      AND COCV8410-REFINVOICE EQUAL SPACES
**AF  *          MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
**AF  *          MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-S
**AF  *          MOVE COCK0001-ZREF-OBRIGAT  TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-MSG
**AF  *          MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
**AF  *                                   TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
**AF  *      END-IF
**AF  *    END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV8410-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATDP-PAG
               IF COCV8410-DDATEPAG EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN OR
                  COCV8410-DDATEPAG EQUAL SPACES
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DPAG-OBRIGAT TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV8410-DDATAEMIS2 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               IF COCV8410-DDATEDUE EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-DDATEDUE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DVENC-OBRIGAT TO COCV8411-DDATEDUE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8411-DDATEDUE-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV8410-DDATAEMIS2 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               IF COCV8410-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                  COCV8410-CSTATUS EQUAL SPACES
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DEMIS-STATUS-INVD
                   TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV8411-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
      *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *      IF (COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT  < ZEROS   AND
      *          COCV8410-NTAXAMOUNT    > ZEROS)   OR
      *         (COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT  > ZEROS   AND
      *          COCV8410-NTAXAMOUNT    < ZEROS)
      *        MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *        MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-NTAXAMOUNT-S
      *        MOVE COCK0001-SINAL-ERRADO  TO COCV8411-NTAXAMOUNT-MSG
      *        MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8411-NTAXAMOUNT-CAPLIC
      *      END-IF
      *    END-IF.
      *
      *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *     IF COCV8410-CIMPOSTO    NOT EQUAL SPACES AND
      *        COCV8410-NTAXAMOUNT      EQUAL ZEROS
      *        MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *        MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-NTAXAMOUNT-S
      *        MOVE COCK0001-VALOR-OBRIGAT TO COCV8411-NTAXAMOUNT-MSG
      *        MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8411-NTAXAMOUNT-CAPLIC
      *     END-IF
      *    END-IF.
      *
      *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *      IF COCV8410-CIMPOSTO        EQUAL SPACES AND
      *         COCV8410-NTAXAMOUNT  NOT EQUAL ZEROS
      *         MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *         MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-S
      *         MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-MSG
      *         MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-CAPLIC
      *      END-IF
      *    END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV8410-CPRAZO          EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-CPRAZO-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV8411-CPRAZO-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8411-CPRAZO-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT    NOT EQUAL ZEROS
             AND COCV8410-CIMPOSTO        EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV8410-CMOEDA EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-CMOEDA-S
                MOVE COCK0001-MOEDA-OBRIGAT TO COCV8411-CMOEDA-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8411-CMOEDA-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.
**AF  *
**AF  * Deixa de obrigar a preencher a referencia
**AF  *
**AF  *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
**AF  *      IF COCV8410-DDATAEMIS2 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
**AF  *        IF COCV8410-REFINVOICE EQUAL SPACES
**AF  *          MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
**AF  *          MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-S
**AF  *          MOVE COCK0001-ZREF-OBRIGAT  TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-MSG
**AF  *          MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
**AF  *                                   TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
**AF  *        END-IF
**AF  *      END-IF
**AF  *    END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF COCV8410-CTIPFAC EQUAL SPACES
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV8411-CTIPFAC-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CTIPDSP-OBRIGAT TO COCV8411-CTIPFAC-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                           TO COCV8411-CTIPFAC-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV8410-DDATEPAG NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               IF COCV8410-DDATEPAG < COCV8410-DDATAEMISS
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO COCV8411-DDATEPAG-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DDATEPAG-MENOR-DSP
                                           TO COCV8411-DDATEPAG-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                           TO COCV8411-DDATEPAG-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *---------------------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Valida se a Referencia da Factura já existe no mesmo    ---*
      *--- Fornecedor.                                             ---*
      *---------------------------------------------------------------*
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV8410-REFINVOICE NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE ZEROS                 TO COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
              MOVE COCV8410-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
              MOVE COCV8410-REFINVOICE   TO COCD6702-GREFINV
      *       MOVE COCV8410-CMOEDA       TO COCD6702-CMOEDA
              MOVE COCV8410-GFORNECED     TO COCD6702-GCLIENTE

              EXEC SQL
                   SELECT NIDINVOICE
                    INTO  :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                     FROM  COVT6702_EXPENSES
                    WHERE  GREFINV     = :COCD6702-GREFINV
                      AND  GCLIENTE    = :COCD6702-GCLIENTE
      *               AND  CMOEDA      = :COCD6702-CMOEDA
      **R             AND  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
**AF  * Volta a considerar o NIDPROJECTO ao verificar duplicado
**AF                  AND  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
      **R             FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
              END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-COVT6702  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF VIAW0005-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-REF-JA-EXISTE-FORN
                                           TO COCV8411-REFINVOICE-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                           TO COCV8411-DDATEPAG-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT    TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
           MOVE COCV8410-CIMPOSTO        TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
           MOVE COCV8410-CMOEDA          TO COCL5005-CMOEDA
           MOVE COCD3605-PAIS            TO COCL5005-CPAIS
           MOVE ZEROS                    TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
           MOVE ZEROS                    TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
           MOVE ZEROS                    TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
           MOVE COCK0002-EVEN-DESPESA    TO COCL5005-CTIP-EVEN
           MOVE COCD3605-CEMPRESA        TO COCL5005-CEMPRESA
           MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO     TO COCL5005-NIDPROJECTO
           MOVE COCV8410-NIDINVOICE      TO COCL5005-NIDINVOICE
           MOVE COCV8410-GFORNECED       TO COCL5005-GFORNECED

           MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS.

           IF  COCV8410-DDATAEMISS NOT = SPACES AND
               COCV8410-DDATAEMISS NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV8410-DDATAEMISS  TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
           END-IF.

           IF  COCV8410-DDATAEMIS2 NOT = SPACES AND
               COCV8410-DDATAEMIS2 NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV8410-DDATAEMIS2  TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ETCL0002-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                              ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

           INITIALIZE ETCL0002-AREA-ERRO REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                              ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT

           PERFORM COCP5005-CALL-ROTINA
              THRU COCP5005-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT

           PERFORM ETCP0002-STD-END
              THRU ETCP0002-STD-END-EXIT

           IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
             MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
             MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-S
             MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO       TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-MSG
             MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO   TO COCV8411-CIMPOSTO-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'COCL5005-NRETTAX   ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE  COCL5005-NRETTAX     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-INSERE-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-INSERE-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-INSERE-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8410-NIDINVOICE    TO COCD6702-NIDINVOICE  .
           MOVE COCV8410-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO .
           MOVE COCV8410-GFORNECED     TO COCD6702-GCLIENTE     .
           MOVE COCV8410-DDATAINSER    TO COCD6702-DDATAINSER  .
           MOVE COCV8410-DDATAEMISS    TO COCD6702-DDATAEMISS  .
           MOVE COCV8410-DDATAEMIS2    TO COCD6702-DDATAEMIS2  .
           MOVE COCV8410-DDATEDUE      TO COCD6702-DDATEDUE    .
           MOVE COCV8410-CPRAZO        TO COCD6702-CPRAZO      .

           IF  COCV8410-MVOR = ZEROS
               MOVE COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO COCD6702-MVOR
           ELSE
               MOVE COCV8410-MVOR          TO COCD6702-MVOR
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT.

           MOVE COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCD6702-NTAXAMOUNT  .
           MOVE COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCV8411-NTAXAMOUNT  .

           MOVE COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT    TO COCD6702-NTOTRET     .
           MOVE COCL5005-NRETTAX       TO COCD6702-NTAXRET     .

           MOVE COCV8410-GDESCINVOICE  TO COCD6702-GDESCINVOICE.

           IF COCV8410-CSTATUS EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM TO COCV8410-CSTATUS
           END-IF

           MOVE COCV8410-CSTATUS       TO COCD6702-CSTATUS     .
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I    TO COCD6702-CUSERID     .
           MOVE COCV8410-REFINVOICE    TO COCD6702-GREFINV     .
           MOVE COCV8410-DDATEPAG      TO COCD6702-DPAG        .
           MOVE COCV8410-CMOEDA        TO COCD6702-CMOEDA      .
           MOVE COCV8410-CIMPOSTO      TO COCD6702-CIMPOSTO    .
           MOVE COCV8410-NOTAS         TO COCD6702-NOTAS       .
           MOVE COCV8410-CTIPFAC       TO COCD6702-CTIPFAC     .
           MOVE COCV8410-CIBAN         TO COCD6702-CIBAN       .
           MOVE ZEROS                  TO COCD6702-MVORCTRV    .

           COMPUTE COCV8411-NVALTOT  = COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT +
                                       COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT

           MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCD6702-NTOTPAG.
           MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCD6702-NTAXPAG.
           MOVE COCV8410-PROJDSP       TO COCD6702-PROJDSP     .

           IF COCV8410-NTOTALAMOUNT < 0
              MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO TO COCD6702-CTIPDOC
           ELSE
              MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA      TO COCD6702-CTIPDOC
           END-IF.

           COMPUTE COCV8411-NVALLIQ  = COCV8411-NVALTOT      -
                                      (COCV8411-NVALREC      +
                                       COCV8411-NTAXREC)     -
                                      (COCD6702-NTOTRET      +
                                       COCD6702-NTAXRET).

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS

              EXEC SQL
                   INSERT INTO COVT6702_EXPENSES
                   (
                      NIDINVOICE
                    , NIDPROJECTO
                    , GCLIENTE
                    , DDATAINSER
                    , DDATAEMISS
                    , DDATAEMIS2
                    , DDATEDUE
                    , CPRAZO
                    , NTOTALAMOUNT
                    , NTAXAMOUNT
                    , GDESCINVOICE
                    , CSTATUS
                    , CUSERID
                    , HTIMEST
                    , GREFINV
                    , DPAG
                    , CTIPDOC
                    , CMOEDA
                    , CIMPOSTO
                    , NOTAS
                    , CTIPFAC
                    , NTOTPAG
                    , NTAXPAG
                    , NTOTRET
                    , NTAXRET
                    , CIBAN
                    , MVOR
                    , MVORCTRV
                    , PROJDSP
                   )
                   VALUES (
                          :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                        , :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                        , :COCD6702-GCLIENTE
                        , :COCD6702-DDATAINSER
                        , :COCD6702-DDATAEMISS
                        , :COCD6702-DDATAEMIS2
                        , :COCD6702-DDATEDUE
                        , :COCD6702-CPRAZO
                        , :COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
                        , :COCD6702-NTAXAMOUNT
                        , :COCD6702-GDESCINVOICE
                        , :COCD6702-CSTATUS
                        , :COCD6702-CUSERID
                        ,  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                        , :COCD6702-GREFINV
                        , :COCD6702-DPAG
                        , :COCD6702-CTIPDOC
                        , :COCD6702-CMOEDA
                        , :COCD6702-CIMPOSTO
                        , :COCD6702-NOTAS
                        , :COCD6702-CTIPFAC
                        , :COCD6702-NTOTPAG
                        , :COCD6702-NTAXPAG
                        , :COCD6702-NTOTRET
                        , :COCD6702-NTAXRET
                        , :COCD6702-CIBAN
                        , :COCD6702-MVOR
                        , :COCD6702-MVORCTRV
                        , :COCD6702-PROJDSP
                   )
              END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-COVT6702               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-DUPREC
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                      MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                        TO COCV8411-NIDINVOICE-S
                      MOVE COCK0001-NIDDSP-A-EXISTS
                        TO COCV8411-NIDINVOICE-MSG
                      MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                        TO COCV8411-NIDINVOICE-CAPLIC
                 ELSE
                    IF NOT DB2-OK
                       MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2299-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8411-MSG         TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV8411-LENGTH      TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8411-NR-CAMPOS   TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES               TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY COCP5005.
           COPY ETCP0002.
           COPY AQCP0005.
